Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶然注意到的事情　令人震惊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.48,0:00:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回顾以前的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.82,0:00:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一去不返的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.61,0:00:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不似想像中的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今以后就可以和你一起渡过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无怨无悔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论现在还是未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.55,0:00:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是发生过那时候的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.97,0:00:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从注意到之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今以后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以　还是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.40,0:00:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想在这里和你相见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,, 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据这份报告
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只知道嫌疑犯行踪不明是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经申请搜索令搜查过嫌疑犯的公寓了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说那是未经过检验的枪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过　它确实被用做刹人凶器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以说一下我个人看法吗？森川警官
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请讲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实发生了刹人事件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这已经不是一课应该管的事了　没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是　是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你们是不打算放手这个案子了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:04:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就这样吧\N此案以四课为主　你们两个协助调查
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:03.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专门布署的大搜查　真是佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啍　你还在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是采用了一课的搜查方案
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是那枝枪的新持有者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:38.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别太过份好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦　你在关心我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我谁也不关心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了　下次有事情时就叫我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神滩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你藏着什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不巧　我是个善良的平民呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家庭有一点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都清楚　但是都没有说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是没有血缘关系的家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家庭　这样的组成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么意义呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优　从今天开始\N这个人就是你的母亲了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近　优越来越像父亲了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是　是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没什么太大的感觉\N父亲是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　当然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优　长大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越来越像他父亲了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？不继续吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让妈妈看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优　你很想要这样做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈　为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎啊　刚才没有把我当成母亲的人是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是真正的母亲的话\N就不会想要做这种事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果　无论在一起生活了多少年\N外人还是外人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊嗯！？\N忘记了一点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你一个人先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈　妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优　不要叫我妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美佐子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优　再来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀　遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优　好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是坏孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此　就是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,X 那边　已经传达到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啍　那个小兔崽子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么怎么办　这是我的枪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊　会发生什么呢\N我很感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:15:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不感兴趣吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个　森川　你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是　嫌疑犯那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是巡逻一下罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来离升职又有一段距离了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎啊　你那么想升职啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么今天缺席又没打电话请假呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是优的班导师水谷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　老师　真是麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起　久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好　老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身体已经没事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那．．．那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天　已经见到优了\N所以．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师　不要这么急
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀　老师不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优　怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.84,0:19:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和美佐子的感觉不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射到里面可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不．．．不要\N不要射到里面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优　做你想做的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就射到里面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样　优\N喜欢吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:08.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有小孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师　小孩是我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.65,0:21:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射到里面了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优的孩子不能让这个女人生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优的孩子是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.11,0:22:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们再来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.13,0:22:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才有枪声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.12,0:23:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.87,0:23:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是“猎人”吗？　你不认识我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.12,0:23:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是和你有同样目标的“天使”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.62,0:23:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦　没听过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.13,0:23:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你又为什么在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.80,0:23:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来拿回忘记的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.82,0:23:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.13,0:24:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.89,0:24:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在进去会被刹的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.89,0:25:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把枪的传言是？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.11,0:25:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让持有者疯狂的诅咒之枪　是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.40,0:25:13.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么　“猎人”
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.15,0:25:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在是正常的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.16,0:25:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎么样